law.text:
A person may not sell or deliver shell eggs to a distributor, retailer, or food service facility unless at the time of delivery the person furnishes an invoice delivery ticket accurately detailing the sale of the shell eggs pursuant to this section. Every invoice delivery ticket shall contain upon its face the following information:
Delivery date;
Name and address of the seller;
Name and address of the purchaser;
The registration number, if any, of the purchaser;
The quantity;
The grade and size of the shell eggs delivered; and
The inspection fee, if applicable.
